  "title": "Staff Nurse (Office Hours)",
  "description": "<h5>Job Description &amp; Requirements</h5>\n<ol>\n  <li>General nursing duties in clinic which include preparing patients for their health screening or radiology services</li>\n  <li>To assist doctor during consultation or in any procedures / treatment</li>\n  <li>Handle any registeration, appointment bookings and answer any phone call enquiries</li>\n  <li>Follow up with patients on any feedback / concerns that they may have</li>\n  <li>Interact and coordinate with different teams to ensure that the centre's operations is running smoothly and efficiently</li>\n  <li>Maintain the cleanliness and readiness of all equipment / instruments</li>\n  <li>Assist in collating patients' medical results and documents any patient assessment findings and progress</li>\n  <li>Provide administrative support to the department when required</li>\n  <li>Any other adhoc duties as assigned by the Wellness Manager</li>\n  <li>Recognized qualification in nursing field</li>\n  <li>Candidates with blood taking or iv cannulation experience will have added advantage</li>\n  <li>At least 2 year(s) of working experience in related field is required for this position with <u><strong>scope experience</strong></u></li>\n  <li>Good communication and interpersonal skill</li>\n  <li>Strong team player</li>\n  <li>5.5 days work week (Monday to Friday; Half Saturday)</li>\n  <li>Location: Lucky Plaza</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Applicants who are interested in this role are invited to apply with their comprehensive resume with full details via <strong>\"Apply Now\" </strong>button. Only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</p>",
